modName: Elean lvl 1 thief mage Save Game
descriptionHtml:
Female lvl 1 Thief/Mage Character. Joined to thieves guild and mage guild. 

Version 4: Imperial
- Full fur armor set
- Shrouded hood
- Nightingale hood
- Shrouded shoes
- Shrouded hand wraps
- 2 iron daggers
- Novice robes and hood
- Spelltomes: Magelight, Fury, Courage
- Spells: Sparks, healing, flames and conjure flame athronach

Version 3: Nord
- Full fur armor set
- 2 iron daggers
- Novice robes and hood
- Ring of minor conjuration and illusion 
- Spell tome of magelight, raise zombie 
- Mage Circlet (version 3)
- Nightweavers band (version 3)
- Spells: Sparks, healing, flames, conjure flame athronac,h Fury 

Version 2: Nord
- Full fur armor set
- 2 iron daggers
- Ring of minor conjuration and illusion
- Spell tome of magelight, raise zombie 
- Chefs Hat 
- Staff of Calm
- Skills: Sneak, Lockpicking and Pickpocket all raised to 40 

Version 1: Nord
- Full fur armor set
- 2 iron daggers
- Sparks, healing, flames and conjure flame athronach. 


Sven as a companion. Starting location is Solitude.

Mods used and install order (version 3):
- Xenius Character Enhancement 
- Better Females by Bella (only eyebrows)
- Covereyes
- Pretty Lips
- Dalls Skyrim Nords (body)
- Straight Hair Retexture
- Coolsims Hairpack Retexture

Started just new game so i figured, why not make a save game and upload here :b
